{"TopicId":128297,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Making Mods","CreatedByName":"George2004","CreatedById":154303,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-20T22:16:28Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"George2004","CreatedById":154303,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-20T22:16:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi I was wondering if anybody could tell me how to make mods! Answers will be greatly appreciated!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gelix","CreatedById":154833,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-20T22:43:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was wondering the same thing! \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/154303-george2004/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022154303\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/154303-george2004/\u0022\u003E@George2004\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0The link to my post is \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/128291-suggestions-for-new-modders/\u0022\u003Ehere\u003C/a\u003E !\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"George2004","CreatedById":154303,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-21T15:18:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs someone going to answer me or not?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CobaltWolf","CreatedById":105588,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-21T16:53:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222331209\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022128297\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221450711127\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154303\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022George2004\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, George2004 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs someone going to answer me or not?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/85372-mod-development-links-compilation-some-links-do-not-work-formatting-broken/\u0022\u003EProlly not, tbh.\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Randazzo","CreatedById":136468,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-21T17:05:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222331209\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022128297\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221450711127\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154303\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022George2004\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, George2004 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs someone going to answer me or not?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYour question is way too broad, and the answer would be\u00A0complicated. Basically you need to:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nLearn to create 3d models (Blender, SketchUp, Wings 3D, etc)\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nLearn to UV map those models\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nLearn to create textures\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nLearn to use Unity to export those Models \u002B Textures into a Mu file\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nLearn to create a config to go along with your model\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nOptional - Learn to code C# to create custom modules for your parts.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nSimple right? See \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/127856-modding-ksp-making-3d-game-modelsis-it-worth-the-trouble/\u0026amp;do=findComment\u0026amp;comment=2322574\u0022\u003EHERE\u003C/a\u003E for slightly more details, and check out the Development links compilation thread as well. You will need to do the homework yourself for the most part though. If you hit a snag, you can always come here for help.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-12-21T17:06:32Z\u0022 title=\u002212/21/2015 05:06  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 21, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by Randazzo\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"George2004","CreatedById":154303,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-21T18:44:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m sorry about the qst. being too broad! Thanks for the info!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}